1
00:00:00,280 --> 00:00:01,280
Hinata!

2
00:00:01,640 --> 00:00:03,280
Mizuki said he's dropping out of the school festival.

3
00:00:03,680 --> 00:00:04,680
What?

4
00:00:04,760 --> 00:00:05,760
What do you mean?

5
00:00:05,760 --> 00:00:07,240
I'm not sure myself.

6
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:08,400
Look!

7
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,280
He just sent this message out of the blue...

8
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:16,400
(Mizuki: Sorry, I can't perform. I won't be at the festival either.)

9
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,440
What the hell...

10
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:20,640
The festival is tomorrow...

11
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:23,280
Mizuki didn't even show up to school.

12
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,600
What are we supposed to do now?

13
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:33,280
What is your problem?

14
00:00:33,680 --> 00:00:36,120
I'm just feeling under the weather and taking a sick day.

15
00:00:36,120 --> 00:00:37,480
That's not what I'm asking.

16
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:40,360
I'm asking why you're skipping the festival!

17
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:41,360
It's nothing.

18
00:00:42,440 --> 00:00:43,760
I just lost interest, that's all.

19
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:45,880
The play and all that...

20
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:47,840
Excuse me?

21
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:50,000
Everyone has been working so hard on this.

22
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,400
And besides,

23
00:00:52,400 --> 00:00:53,720
You seemed to be enjoying the rehearsals before.

24
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:55,320
I was just playing along.

25
00:00:58,060 --> 00:00:59,360
I told you already, didn't I?

26
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:03,560
Stay out of my business.

27
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,560
What kind of attitude is that?

28
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,640
I'm moving out after graduation anyway.

29
00:01:08,520 --> 00:01:09,880
Playing the role of a big brother for a while...

30
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:11,720
Sorry about that.

31
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:13,920
Why are you doing this?

32
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,920
Don't mess with me.

33
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,720
You were the one who insisted I call you brother.

34
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:22,040
It felt weird at first,

35
00:01:23,640 --> 00:01:26,600
but you're actually kind,

36
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:28,880
and you've been so reliable.

37
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:35,280
So what is this now?

38
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:38,720
I have no idea what's going on in your head.

39
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:43,400
Stop messing with my head.

40
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,520
Hinata-kun.

41
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,680
Is something wrong?

42
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,800
Uncle...

43
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:15,520
Please, tell me the truth about Mizuki.
